<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4730&amp;p=41767#p41767"><![CDATA[
Most instructions affect only a subset of the flags, leaving the others untouched. The various documents should cover this. Clear all flags before every instruction only if you want an incorrect emulator. <img src="http://forums.nesdev.com/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Mon Jan 12, 2009 4:28 am</p><hr />
